<section class="about-project-section">
  <div class="about-project-container">
    <h3 class="project-topics">About Grassroots</h3>
    <p>The project scope was fairly strightforward. I was tasked to create a page that would allow users to login with their Spotify account, and then display their top artists in a grid. The grid would have a resize effect that would allow the user to see more information about the artist when they hover over the image. With this feature in place that would allow for testing on users before implementing future features.
    </p>
    <div class="language-icons">
      <i class="fa-brands fa-html5"></i>
      <i class="fa-brands fa-sass"></i>
